name: Noemi Brow Gel Dye, 10ml
description:
Noemi Dye Gel – The Future of Eyebrow Color

After 1.6 years of intensive research, we proudly present the liquid version of our successful Noemi Dye Cream: Noemi Dye Gel. This innovative eyebrow dye combines nourishing ingredients and high-quality color to strengthen and care for the eyebrows and guarantee a long-lasting, intense color.

Liquid Dye - The world's first real liquid hybrid color with nutrients and unique nuances that are second to none!

Special ingredients and their effects:

Hydrolyzed corn protein: Supports the strengthening and restructuring of eyebrow hairs, reduces hair breakage, and improves texture.
Hydrolyzed Soy Protein: Increases elasticity and moisture of the hairs, strengthens them, and reduces brittleness, resulting in fuller, defined eyebrows.
Hydrolyzed wheat protein: moisturizes, softens, and gives eyebrows a natural shine.
Lemon peel oil: Cleanses and clarifies eyebrows, promotes healthy growth, and gives the color a natural shine.
Niacinamide (Vitamin B3): Promotes the growth of healthy eyebrows, strengthens hair follicles and reduces pigment loss, allowing for more intense and longer-lasting color.
Application and flexibility:

Noemi Dye Gel can be ideally combined with the Noemi Cream and Gel Developer and, in conjunction with the Noemi Dye Cream and the Noemi Clear Corrector, offers countless possibilities for individual color creations.

The result is well-groomed, strengthened eyebrows with intense and long-lasting color - ideal for anyone looking for high-quality and nourishing coloring.
short_description:
The Noemi Dye are hybrid colors. Due to the perfect composition of the colors, it finally simplifies the coloring of eyebrows and eyelashes. The colors can be used 100% pure without getting an unwanted yellow, red or green tint. The colors can also be mixed with each other to obtain special mixtures. In addition, they do not darken the eyebrows, because the color lightens the natural hair 1-2 shades beforehand. So you always have the perfect and desired result.

Advantages of this hybrid color are that it conditions and colors the hair. It protects against hair breakage, gives fullness, shine and stimulates hair growth. It leaves a tattoo effect on the skin. The colors contain henna extract, olive oil, green tea and aloe vera.

The Noemi Clear is a neutral color corrector. It can be added to any other shade to lighten the colors and it can also be used to enhance the hair and give it extra shine.

With an exposure time of 10 minutes, you get a natural effect that is completely sufficient for coloring the eyebrows.
With an exposure time of 15 minutes, you get an intensive effect on the skin.

Mixing ratio: 1:1 (Solution : Dye)

Exposure time 10 – 15 min.

With an exposure time of 10 minutes, you get a natural effect that is completely sufficient for coloring the eyebrows.

With an exposure time of 15 minutes, you get an intensive effect on the skin.

name: Noemi PreDyed Thread Black, 20m

The pre-colored thread makes it easier to model the eyebrows before coloring. Take as much as needed from the can and get started. You will be able to draw precise and clean lines.

The container holds 20m of the thread.

name: LB Brow Therapy Caring Oil
description: LB Brow Therapy Natural Therapeutic Eyebrow Care Oil. LB BROW THERAPY Natural Therapeutic Eyebrow Care Oil. Therapeutic complex of natural oils for the treatment and SPA-care of eyebrows. A unique combination of 11 oils that can become part of the daily SPA ritual, as well as an effective tool for treating eyebrows after improper procedures. Brow Therapy is a biotherapy for the effective recovery of worn out, brittle, thin and naughty eyebrows damaged by bad lamination, long-term stacking or frequent bleaching. Non-standard, rich, and yet uncongested composition provides multi-care:. - strengthening and restoring the roots and structure of hair;. - nutrition, moisturizing and hair growth stimulation;. - toning and skin care;. - hair softening to facilitate daily styling;. - maintaining the color brightness of the hair after coloring;. Optimal volume and convenient applicator make the daily use of the product as comfortable as possible: you do not need additional tools to apply, the oil will be used sparingly. The pleasant aroma will give pleasure to use, turning daily eyebrow care into a real SPA ritual. The felt applicator allows you to control the amount of product applied and has a massage effect, thus enhancing the effect of new hair growth.

name: LB Next Lash Lift Set NOT GLUE, 14ml
description:
A set of professional products for the lamination procedure without glue using the no-glue technique.

The set includes:
1. Fixing powder for eyelash lamination LB Next NOT GLUE (3g) - 1 pc
2. Lamination Solution No. 1 LB Next "Lifting Balm" (1.5 ml) - 3 pcs

Composition for lamination No. 2 LB Next "Volumising Fix" (1.5 ml) - 3 pcs

Composition for lamination No. 3 LB Next "Moisturising Serum" (1.5 ml) - 3 pcs

The new exclusive lamination product - the fixing powder from the LB Next brand "NOT GLUE" - gives the lash lift artist the ability to perform lamination in just 20 minutes, achieving excellent results on any eyelashes!

The NOT GLUE powder is a new chapter in the history of lamination, where the procedure is performed without glue, without application, and as quickly as possible!

NOT GLUE powder:
- allows working in the technique without the initial application of lashes and performing 3 times more procedures per day
- works with any compositions
- very easy to use: easily mixes with the composition, conveniently applies without damaging the lashes, and quickly cleans up
- provides trouble-free and reliable fixation of all types of lashes on the silicone shield, even dense, resilient, or short ones

In addition, one jar of powder is used as economically as possible, replacing 7 bottles of glue, and the cost of the procedure becomes lower.

description:

Katya Vinog continues to push the boundaries of lash lift techniques with yet another groundbreaking innovation that combines both functionality and aesthetics. The Lower Lash Lift Shields Cats by Katya Vinog is a must have shield that will add an adorable and playful aesthetic to your content!

These rollers are designed with a wide surface that can be applied similar to an eye patch, while simultaneously acting as a bottom lash lift shield for tinting and curling. This 2 in 1 functionality offers unmatched versatility and comfort for a seamless experience.

Crafted from premium silicone with a darling cat imprint, the flexible bend is designed to fit all eye shapes, delivering consistent results for all your clients. These shields are available in fun and vibrant colours for medium to long lower lashes.

The Bottom Lash Lift Shields Cats is the perfect complement to a lash lift service allowing for a double lash lift, thereby maximizing the service, and spicing up your content even further.

Size: One size - medium to long lashes

Qty: 1 pair

name: Katya Vinog Reusable Sticky Eyepatches BOW - 1 pair BLACK
description:
The black patches serve dual functions by aiding in the isolation of lower lashes during lamination and can be easily removed before dyeing. The inner corners of the patches feature a beveled design for easy access and isolation of the inner lashes. These patches do not need additional fixation during application, allowing for maximum comfort for the client.

Crafted with premium silicone, these sticky patches effectively prevent allergies and skin irritation, making them ideal for sensitive skin and clients prone to hydrogel patch allergies. Furthermore, their versatility allows them to conform to any eye shape and can even be used for lash mapping.

Ideal for eyelash extensions as well as lash lift.
Patches can be marked/drawn on.
Perfect for separating lower lashes.
Slanted edge provides comfort for inner lashes.
The patches stick to the skin on their own without glue.
Suitable for any eye shape.
Made of premium silicone, suitable for sensitive and allergy-prone skin.

How to re-use:

NOT suitable for autoclave/thermal disinfection

Wash with antibacterial soap
Soak in disinfectant liquid
Rinse with water, ensuring all disinfection liquid is removed
Dry on a flat surface
Not recommended to tint lashes on the patches as they may stain.

name: BrowXenna LUME' Hybrid Gel Tint For Brows
description:
Lumé BrowXenna® — the world's first direct-action gel dyes, specifically created for eyebrow tinting!

This is a product from a professional brand, designed for use by both professionals and at home by every woman. No oxidizer addition required. Minimum procedure time - instant results on the skin!

The pigments have a pleasant scent and are very convenient to work with — they do not spread. They contain a powerful complex of caring components: they do not dry out the skin or hair.

Lumé BrowXenna® can also be added to any semi-permanent dye to adjust the temperature and saturation of the shade: to make it warmer or cooler.

Contraindications:
Individual intolerance to the product's components.
Open wounds and skin damage.
Pregnancy and breastfeeding.
Chronic skin conditions.
It is recommended to perform a sensitivity test before use.

WARNING!
For professional use only. Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with eyes and mucous membranes. In case of eye contact, rinse thoroughly with water and seek medical attention.

Shelf life: 36 months

Shelf life after opening: 6 months

Amount of applications: to 40

METHOD OF APPLICATION
Thoroughly cleanse the skin, you can use the BrowXenna® Deep Cleansing Shampoo-Foam for eyebrows. If there is flaking, it is recommended to use the BrowXenna® Enzyme Scrub for eyebrows. Rinse off the scrub and/or shampoo residue with BrowXenna® Two-Phase Tonic or warm water.
Apply the dye to the eyebrow in the desired shape. The exposure time varies from 1 to 5 minutes and depends on the desired intensity of the shade. You can apply Lumé in two layers to create a tattoo effect on the skin. The intensity of the imprint on the skin can also be adjusted by the density of the layer. For a more watercolor tinting, you can spread the pigment over the skin using a damp brush/microbrush. Lumé BrowXenna® is ideal for hair-stroke coloring techniques. Try BrowXenna® brushes No. 9, No. 10, No. 11 for hair-stroke techniques in your work.
After the exposure time, wash off the dye with warm water. Do not use shampoo at this stage! If necessary, remove excess pigment from the skin with micellar water.
After tinting, use BrowXenna® Fixing Brow Soap or BrowXenna® Fixing Gel for long-lasting brow styling.

name: Browxenna Mono Step Lamination - Formula For Express lamination of eyebrows and eyelashes
description:
Mono Step - is an innovative express lamination system for eyebrows and eyelashes for brow artists who value time and quality.

One lamination step instead of the usual three.
Cuts procedure time in half.
Universal dual-purpose product suitable for laminating both eyebrows and eyelashes significantly reducing the cost for the master.
Effect of perfectly styled eyebrows and resilient curls on eyelashes up to 6 weeks.
Unique formula that restores and strengthens hair structure.
Cysteine — is the only amino acid capable of forming disulfide bonds in the hair structure. These disulfide bridges determine the shape of our hair and provide reverse deformation after lamination.

Cysteine restores and strengthens the hair structure, helps maintain color after dyeing.

The integrity of the hair structure is also maintained by an active care system, which maximizes protection from moisture loss and brittleness.

Organic macadamia oil has a therapeutic effect on thin and damaged hair. The oil formula contains Omega 3,5,7 particles that help strengthen hair follicles and prevent hair loss.

Wheat hydrolyzed protein perfectly moisturizes, enhances shine, and retains moisture, silk proteins easily settle on the surface of the hair and skin, forming a light protective film without weighing down.

Allantoin is often used in cosmetics for delicate baby and sensitive skin. Intensively moisturizes and softens, helps normalize sebum production, has anti-inflammatory properties - soothes and relieves irritation.

Hydrolyzed Keratin - a reduced molecule of natural keratin. In this form, keratin can penetrate the hair structure, providing powerful protective and moisturizing effects.

Argan Oil nourishes and restores damaged, dry hair, promotes growth, and prevents hair loss.

Aloe Vera Extract moisturizes and nourishes the skin and hair, promotes skin regeneration.

Sodium Hyaluronate has regenerative properties.

Panthenol (Provitamin B5) has pronounced anti-inflammatory and regenerative properties, moisturizes, and closes the cuticle, making hair noticeably smoother and shinier.

Instructions for Eyebrows:
Preparation:

Cleanse the eyebrows using BrowXenna Shampoo-foam for deep cleansing. Rinse the Shampoo thoroughly with water.
Dry the eyebrows.
Application of composition:

Apply Mono Step BrowXenna® evenly on the eyebrows using a synthetic brush or applicator stick.
Distribute the product evenly, giving the hairs the desired direction. It's important not to change the eyebrow growth direction more than 45 degrees from natural.
After the exposure time, remove the product with a damp cotton pad in the direction of hair growth.
Exposure Time::

For thick, coarse, rough, and gray hair: 9-10 minutes. For very coarse hair - up to 12 minutes.
For medium-thickness hair: 7-8 minutes.
For porous, thin hair previously chemically treated: 3-6 minutes.
Lamination is not recommended on severely damaged and recently lightened eyebrows; instead, deep care with P Plex Recovery is recommended.
Eyebrow tinting:

Mix 2.7% Oxygen J2 Cream Activator or 1.8% Oxygen J2 Cream Activator with Oxygen J2 Dye for eyebrows and eyelashes at a 1:1 ratio. To avoid darkening the hair, use Oxygen J2 Cream Diluter.
Exposure time: 7 minutes.
Remove the dye with a damp cotton pad.
Dry the eyebrows.
Care and Recovery:

Apply a few drops of BrowXenna® P Plex Recovery, distribute evenly over the eyebrow hairs.
Do not rinse off the product for 24 hours.
Home Care Recommendations:

Use BrowXenna® SPA Mask or BrowXenna® P Plex Recovery 2 times a week.
Use BrowXenna® BOTEX-X or BrowXenna® BOTEX-X concentrate with ceramides.
Instructions for Eyelashes:
Preparation:

Cleanse the eyelashes using BrowXenna Shampoo-foam for deep cleansing. Rinse the Shampoo thoroughly with water.
Fix a silicone lash lift pads of the required size on the upper eyelid.
Carefully distribute and fix the eyelashes on the pads, following the rules of placement.
If you're using gel-type glue increase the exposure time by 2-3 minutes.
Curl Formation:

Apply BrowXenna® Mono Step to the area of the lash curl formation.
With even movements, apply a small amount of Mono Step to 2/3 of the lash length, stepping back 1-2 mm from the roots and leaving the tips free.
After the exposure time remove the product from the eyelashes with a damp cotton swab.
Exposure Time:
For thick and coarse eyelashes:

10-13 minutes
For medium-thickness, natural, and shiny eyelashes:

8-9 minutes
For thin, porous eyelashes previously chemically treated

5 minutes
Eyelash Tinting

Mix Oxygen J2 Cream-Activator 2.7% or Oxygen J2 Cream-Activator 1.8% with Oxygen J2 Dye for eyebrows and eyelashes in a 1:1 ratio.
Apply the resulting dyeing mixture to the eyelashes.
Exposure time: 7 minutes.
Remove the dye with a cotton swab.
Care and Recovery:

Apply a few drops of BrowXenna® P Plex Recovery distribute evenly over the eyelashes.
Do not rinse off the product for 24 hours.
Home Care Recommendations:

To prevent mechanical disruption of the eyelash curl shape, it is recommended to sleep on your back for the first day.
Use BrowXenna® P Plex Recovery,BrowXenna® BOTEX-X, or BOTEX-X concentrate with ceramides 2-3 times a week.
Contraindications:
Individual intolerance to the product's components.
Open wounds and skin damage.
Pregnancy and breastfeeding.
Chronic skin conditions.
It is recommended to perform a sensitivity test before use.

WARNING!
For professional use only. Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with eyes and mucous membranes. In case of eye contact, rinse thoroughly with water and seek medical attention.

Amount of applications: up to 30 procedures.

Storage conditions: in a dry, cool place, out of reach of children, away from direct sunlight.

Shelf life: 36 months

Shelf life after opening: 6 months

pH level: 9,0 *ph

name: Inlei Brow Lamination
description:
InLei® BROW BOMBER is a revolutionary professional treatment, created for the eyebrows and intended to make the hair of the eyebrow arch obedient, soft, silky and styled.

Save 25% when buy 3 steps as a kit!

How to use:

Clean the client’s eyebrows with InLei® MOUSSE .
Prepare the eyebrows with InLei® SALINE PRETREATMENT .
Comb the eyebrows neatly and / or in the desired direction.
Apply a uniform layer of InLei® BROW LIFT 1 with the help of a brush.
Leave on for the time necessary, based on the thickness of the hair ( 6/12 min ). DO NOT USE THE FILM.
Remove the product with a dry cotton pad .
Afterwards, continue with InLei ® Brow Lock 2
Shape the eyebrows with a -Brush.
Place the hair in the desired shape and position .
Spread InLei® “BROW LOCK 2” – fixing for eyebrows.
Leave on for 5-8 minutes .
Remove the product with a moistened cotton pad .
Continue with the dyeing.
Use Brow Bomber 3 after the perming process (InLei® BROW LIFT 1), fixing (InLei® BROW LOCK 2) and InLei® dyeing .
Squeeze a few drops of the product from the bottle and with the help of a brush / comb, rub the product on the natural eyebrows.
Leave on for 5 minutes .
Remove the excess (if necessary) by dabbing with a tissue.
It does not require rinsing.
BROW BOMBER 3 is a nourishing brow butter that concludes the Brow Bomber treatment!

The Butter Contains:

Macadamia oil that nourishes, hydrates and restructures the hair without weighing it down.
Argan oil that repairs dry and brittle hair.
Almond oil that makes the hair soft and shiny.
Marigold Lipo Extract which has a soothing effect on reddened and inflamed skin.
Chamomile flower extract which is a powerful anti-inflammatory.

Product Details:

100% Made in Italy
Airless bottle , zero waste dispenser
Contains ingredients for skin protection
Content: 30 ml (up to 40 treatments).
For professional use only . Carefully read the leaflet

name: Sculptor Flexi Line Lash Lift Sachet
description:
Take On is the first stage of the FLEXI LINE procedure. This component is used to soften the cuticular layer and create a new curve of eyelashes.

Its feature is a delicate effect on the eyelashes. The panthenol in the composition softens the chemical action, and our secret ingredient – caprine triglyceride maintains the moisture of the eyelashes, preventing the hair from drying out. Has high stability to oxidation. It is particularly useful as an emulsion stabilizer. This property is indispensable for cosmetic products, as it helps to give them a longer shelf life.

Take On has a creamy texture that spreads easily, does not spread, holds its shape and does not go beyond the specified limits.

Cost:
Sachet 1 ml: single dose, enough for 5-6 treatments.
Ophthalmic tube 5 ml: designed for 27-33 procedures.
pH: 9.5-9.8
The exposure time is 7-12 minutes, depending on the initial condition of the eyelashes:

thin, weakened eyelashes: 7-8 minutes
normal eyelashes: 9-10 minutes
dense, thick eyelashes: 11-12 minutes

Twist Out is a neutralizing composition used in the second stage of the FLEXI LINE procedure to fix the new curve/direction of the eyelashes.

The composition of Take On contains arginine, which restores the integrity of the hair shaft, fills the voids formed after the first stage. Eyelashes are completely ready to give them a new shape.

Take On is creamy, pigmented, easily distributed, does not spread, keeps its shape and does not go beyond the specified limits.

Cost:

Sachet 1 ml: single dose, enough for 5-6 treatments.
Ophthalmic tube 5 ml: designed for 27-33 procedures.
pH 3.9-4.3
The exposure time is 5-8 minutes, depending on the initial condition of the eyelashes (but no more than 10 minutes):

thin, weakened eyelashes: 5-6 minutes
normal eyelashes: 6-7 minutes
dense, thick eyelashes: 7-8 minutes

The Top Up neutralizing fixative is specially designed to fix the perfect shape of the curls and the excellent shine of the eyelashes during the FLEXI LINE procedure.

Thanks to the innovative polymer Alkyl Methacrylate Copolymer in the composition, eyelashes are fixed on the curler and easily dry in the given shape. Also, Top Up reliably protects hair from moisture, which allows customers to wash immediately after the procedure!

The unique polymer acting as a film-former improves the resistance of eyelashes to external factors, including moisture.

This product is applied before and after removing the curler, its active components based on keratin proteins gently nourish and moisturize the eyelashes, ensuring full recovery after the action of chemical fixing agents. The product has an excellent renewing formula that maintains the elasticity, smoothness and silkiness of the eyelashes. A complex of amino acids protects eyelashes from various external influences, and vitamins and minerals maintain a natural balance.

Top Up has the texture of a transparent fluid with a light, pleasant aroma and a light sticky effect, which allows you to perfectly fix the eyelashes on the curler, as well as create a fashionable “needle” effect.

Cost:

Sachet 1 ml: single dose, enough for 6-8 procedures.
Ophthalmic tube 5 ml: designed for 30-37 procedures.
pH 5.9-6.2
Exposure time: unlimited.

name: IC Factory Lash Lift
description:
Fast, Safe, Convenient, and Comfortable: The Ultimate Lash Lift Solution
IC Factory Lash Lamination / Lift Kit: Product Details
Why is the IC Factory Lash Lamination / Lift Kit a must-have for lash artists?

FAST: The average exposure time for each composition is just 7 minutes, making the process quick and efficient.

SAFE: Our compositions are free from ammonia, hydrogen peroxide, thioglycolic acid, and its derivatives, ensuring a gentle treatment.

CONVENIENT: We've perfected the consistency based on lash experts' feedback for optimal application and results.

COMFORTABLE: The odorless compositions provide a comfortable experience for both lash artists and their clients.

STABLE: Our compositions are resistant to temperature and humidity changes and can be stored for up to 12 months.

ACTIVE CARE FROM THE FIRST STEP OF LASH LAMINATION:

Hydrolyzed keratin: Penetrates deep into the hairs, restoring and protecting them, and retaining moisture to make them silky smooth.
Sunflower oil: Deeply nourishes eyelashes, making them shiny, smooth, resilient, and protected against environmental factors.
Grape seed oil: Stimulates hair growth, strengthens, moisturizes, and prevents dryness and brittleness.
Jojoba oil: Prevents hairs from becoming brittle, dull, and too porous.
Argan oil: Retains moisture inside eyelashes and protects them from external influences.
Wheat germ oil: Nourishes and restores damaged parts of hair.
Macadamia oil: Promotes growth, prevents hair loss, and nourishes and restores damaged, dry eyelashes.
Castor oil: Deeply nourishes, softens hairs, stimulates their growth, and restores shine.

name: Lamitta Laminator Slide Brush For Lash Lift
description:
The Laminator Slide Lash Lift Brush by Lamitta is the new and improved version of the original Laminator Brush. Patented and designed by Liliya Utivlenova, Lamitta has upgraded the classic design and crafted an even more impressive edition that not only ensures maximum comfort, but also delivers impeccable results.

The title of the name unveils the application method - the brush head features a flat, straight cut design that allows you to slide the brush all over the surface of the eyelashes, from roots to tips, efficiently streamlining the wrapping process. The tip is small, yet constructed with thick strong bristles, especially suitable for the small inner corners.

The brush is designed to let the lash artist switch between horizontal and vertical angles, which facilitate different application techniques: the flat side for wrapping, and the vertical angle for isolation.

The Laminator Slide is also an ideal tool for removing excess glue, while no other tools are needed to complete the wrapping step. If you loved the original Laminator Brush, you will instantly fall in love with the new Laminator Slide, delivering a new level of enhanced performance.

For optimal results, use with Lamitta Fixer, Glue Balm or other appropriate lash lift adhesive.

Length: 17 cm

Brush Tip: 0.3 x 0.3 cm

Benefits:
Can use both sides
Switch between horizontal and vertical positions
Flat, straight cut design
Ideal for medium to short lashes
Perfect for wrapping inner corners
Fast wrapping with original glue, faster with glue balm
No other tools required

How to use:
The brush should slide all over the surface of the eyelashes. Slowly slide the brush from the roots to the tips of the lashes. This is how you achieve the perfect isolation for each lash.

How to Clean: Clean with soapy water and rinse with running hot water to clean the brush head from any residuals. Use sanitizing wipes or special disinfectant solutions. It is allowed to use special antiseptic shampoos for brushes. Do not use dry heat.

name: Inlei - Lash Lift System
description:
Description
InLei Products are for the Canadian market only, according to InLei's policy.

We will not ship to the USA or any other country. If you are outside of Canada, look for local suppliers.

Lash Lift System Bottle by INLEI

The Magical Trio. The revolutionary Lash Lift System by InLei has been entirely structured, tested and produced in Italy. The LASH FILLER® treatment guarantees an average thickening of the natural hair by up to 24% in three treatments. It has been demonstrated and affirmed by the clinical test carried out at the Research Institute of Milan. All While giving the client a lift and curl that will continue to keep the health of the clients lashes.

The original formula of In Lei® “FILLER 3” allows the microparticles of the filler to penetrate into the hair delicately, binding to the keratin fibres of the hair itself. Thanks to the “Three Regeneration” complex, and to the adequate preparation of the lashes with In Lei® “FORM 1” and In Lei® “FIX 2”, it guarantees a stable result and highly effective nourishment and thickening, giving new silkiness to the lashes. The LASH FILLER® treatment can reach the hair bulb, nourish them and work on the hair bulb's structure in the following months after the treatment.

Size: 4ml

Usage: 25-30 applications

PAO: 2M

*Each step is sold individually

FOR PROFESSIONAL USE ONLY

Form 1 - Lash Perm
The Form 1 offers a highly effective yet safe and gentle formula for your client's lashes. The alkaline pH of this solution allows to open the scales of the hair in a fast and refined way, without damaging it and preparing it for the next step.

Fix 2 - Lash Fixing
The formula of the fixing solution allows to "secure" the curvature of the hair following the shape of the shied used. It works safely and quickly, working in perfect sync with the Form 1. Prepares the lecture of eyelashes for the next step, thanks to its perfectly balanced formula with the correct percentage of the active ingredient, hydrogen peroxide.

Designed to work together in perfect tandem in the process of Lash Filler 3, guaranteeing reliable and proven results! When completed as full protocol: Form 1, Fix & Filler 3, you can experience the clinically proven results guaranteeing thickening of natural hair on average up to 24% in three treatments. It defines, nourishes, thickens and strengthens the lash structure, giving color & shine.

Filler 3 - Lash Filler
This magical formula with clinically proven results guarantee a thickening of natural hair on average up to 24% in three treatments. It defines, nourishes, thickens and strengthens the lash structure, giving color & shine.

The "FILLER 3" bonds the keratin fibres of the hair itself by allowing the microparticles of the filler to penetrate inside the hair gently. Furthermore, it has the ability to reach up to the hair bulb, feeding them and also working in the following months after the application on the structure of the hair bulb,

For maximal results and as confirmed by the clinical test, combine with Inlei "Form 1" & "Fix 2".

Benefits
Clinically proven results
Nourishes, thickens and gives new silkiness
Only use what you need, no unnecessary waste

How to Use
1) Clean and prep the lashes with InLei Mousse and Saline Pre-Treatment.

2) Lift the lashes onto the chosen shield with the help of the Helper 2.0 and Fixing Gel or Lamica Gel.

3) Take a small scoop out of Form 1 with a Mister Fix Scoop (one comes in every box of tint).

4) Apply Form 1 in a perfect linear line across the lashes with the Vincent Brush. Allow setting correct time below.

Form 1 Processing Times:

Thin, soft natural lashes- 6-8 minutes
Average/medium thickness of natural lashes- 8-10 minutes
Thick, healthy natural lashes- 10-12 minutes
Super thick and strong natural lashes- 12-14 minutes
5) Remove with the Dry Vincent Brush.

6) Apply Fix 2 the same way as Form 1 but set it for half the time of Form 1 plus one minute. Remove with Vincent Brush.

Fix 2 Processing Time:

Fine hair- 4-5 minutes
Medium hair- 5-6 minutes
Thick hair- 6-7 minutes
Rigid hair- 8-9 minutes
Fix 2 goes on for half the time of Form 1 plus one minute

7) Mix your chosen tint colour with InLei® Developer 1.5% volume. Apply with the Michealangelo Brush and set it for the same time as Fix 2.

8) Remove ALL tints with the Michealangelo Brush and Softies.

9) Apply Filler 3: Dispense with the help of the dropper, small amount of solution onto the eyelashes, after Fix 2 (Step 2) and/or tinting process. Evenly spread, coating the natural lashes fully in the solution and allow the product to penetrate until completely absorbed. This product needs to be penetrated into each lash to receive the famous benefits of the thickening agents and nutrients. Remove with damp cotton swab.

10) Brush out with a Mini Lamination Brush to fan out the lashes after the procedure.

Tips
Bottles are great if you do 3-5 treatments or more a week for the PAO is 2 months. If you do less, we suggest purchasing the sachets.
If you have not tried Inlei Lash Lift System, a one time sample size is available to gain experience with using the system for the first time.
Ingredients
Form 1: Aqua (Water Eau), Ammonium Thioglycolate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lauryl Alcohol, Ceteareth-20, Ceteareth-30, Ammonia, Myristyl Alcohol, Parfum (Fragrance), Tetrasodium Edta

Fix 2: Aqua (Water\Eau), Cetearyl Alcohol, Lauryl Alcohol, Hydrogen Peroxide, Ceteareth-20, Ceteareth-30, Myristyl Alcohol, Etidronic Acid

Filler 3: Aqua (Water\Eau), Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Ppg-5-Ceteth-20, Hydroxypropyl Guar, Parfum (Fragrance), Ethylhexylglycerin, Panthenol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Biotinoyl Tripeptide-1

Made in Italy

description:
01. LIFTING: Exposure time: 6-12 minutes depending on the structure and condition of the eyebrow hairs

03. KERAMASS: Exposure time: from 5 minutes to complete drying on the eyebrow hairs

PH: 5.94

INGREDIENTS: AQUA, GLYCERIN, PEG-40 HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL, HYDROLYZED COLLAGEN, HYDROLYZED PEA PROTEIN, HYDROLYZED VEGETABLE PROTEIN, PHENOXYETHANOL, POLYACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER-6, CYAMOPSI TETRAGONOLOBA GUM, PARFUM, ARGININE, DISODIUM EDTA, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, GLYCINE, HISTIDINE HYDROCHLORIDE, LYSINE HYDROCHLORIDE, TRIFOLIUM PRATENSE/VIGNA RADIATA SPROUT EXTRACT, POTASSIUM SORBATE, SODIUM BENZOATE, LACTIC ACID, ACETYL TETRAPEPTIDE-5

04. CALMING: Exposure time: unlimited

RH: oil

INGREDIENTS: ISOPROPYL MYRISTATE, DICAPRYLYL ETHER, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL, PRUNUS AVIUM SEED OIL, TOCOPHEROL, CHAMOMILLA RECUTITA FLOWER EXTRACT, CRAMBE ABYSSINICA SEED OIL, PERSEA GRATISSIMA OIL, ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF EXTRACT, RICINUS COMMUNIS OIL, HELIANTHUS ANNUUS SEED OIL, ETHYL LINOLEATE, ETHYL OLEATE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE, DIMETHICONE, PARFUM

PROTOCOL OF EYEBROW LAMINATION WITH FLEXI LINE BROW COMPONENTS:

1. EYEBROW CLEANING

2. APPLICATION OF INGREDIENT #1 – LIFTING. Squeeze the compound onto a glove, into a glass/plastic container, or into a SCULPTOR silicone palette (metal containers are prohibited). Using a silicone or synthetic brush, apply the product to the eyebrows, starting from the head in the direction of the body and tail. It is advisable to immediately set the required direction of the hairs when applying. Choose the exposure time depending on the density of the eyebrows, the porosity of the hairs, the change in the artificial direction of the hairs compared to the natural one.

Keep the component on the eyebrows for:

6-8 minutes on thin hairs

8-10 minutes on medium

10-12 minutes for thick

After the exposure time has elapsed, remove the drug with a dry cotton pad without stretching the skin or pulling the hairs, so as not to injure them. If there are hairs that are not in the desired direction, use a brush or a brush to lay them out as needed for laying out eyebrows. Since there can be different types of hairs on different parts of the eyebrow, the drug can be removed locally, and component #2 – Fixing can be applied immediately to the corresponding areas. This will stop the reaction and not damage the hairs further while waiting for the removal of the permanent component from other parts of the eyebrows.

3. APPLICATION OF COMPONENT #2 – FIXING. Squeeze the compound onto a glove, into a glass/plastic container, or into a SCULPTOR silicone palette (metal containers are prohibited). With the help of a silicone or synthetic brush, apply the preparation to the eyebrows, starting from the head in the direction of the body and tail, or in the sequence in which component No. 1 - Lifting was removed locally. Select the exposure time.

Keep the component on the eyebrows for:

7-8 minutes on fine hairs

8-10 minutes on medium

10-12 minutes on thick.

After the exposure time has elapsed, remove the drug with a wet cotton pad in the direction of hair growth. Dry the eyebrows with a dry cotton pad.

4. APPLICATION OF INGREDIENT #3 – KERAMASS. Put the ingredient in a glass/plastic container or in a SCULPTOR silicone palette. Using a brush or a nylon brush, apply the product to the eyebrows. Wait at least 5 minutes or until the product is completely dry, if there is a lot of it, remove the residue with a wet cotton pad. If the application was only on the hairs, you can correct and dye the eyebrows without removing the residues. In this way, hair coloring can be achieved without darkening.

5. SHAPING AND CORRECTION OF EYEBROWS. It is recommended to make a correction with tweezers or a mixed correction: tweezers + wax, but apply the wax only in the area where there were no ingredients, so as not to injure the skin with excessively aggressive procedures.

6. EYEBROWS DYEING

7. APPLICATION OF INGREDIENT #4 - CALMING. Squeeze the compound onto a glove, into a glass/plastic container, or into a SCULPTOR silicone palette (metal containers are prohibited). Using a silicone or synthetic brush, apply the product to the eyebrows, starting from the head in the direction of the body and tail. Leave for 5 minutes, after the exposure time has elapsed, remove the residue with a dry tissue or leave it on the client's eyebrows until completely absorbed.

EXPIRY DATE: 3 years from the date of manufacture EXPIRY DATE AFTER OPENING: Medicines in sachets are recommended to be used immediately after opening.

name: Mia Pro Lashes Lamitab Palette For Lash Lift
description:
Smart Lash Lift Procedure Organizer by MIA PRO LASHES

The Lamitab Pro Palette by MIA PRO LASHES reduces brow and lash lamination procedure time by minimizing manipulations with glue and paint compositions, while simultaneously organizing and simplifying the order of your tools. Every detail of the Pro Palette is carefully crafted with the intent of optimizing the lash artist's productivity and streamlining their workflow. The Lamitab Pro Palette by MIA PRO LASHES has already gained appreciation by TOP experts in the world of Lash Lifts.

 

The luxe silicone and cutting-edge soft touch surface provide effortless access to your supplies, while the detailed working algorithm leads you in creating flawless brows and lashes without any mess. The palette also ensures the perfect quantity of solutions for every procedure, preventing excess product waste. It features an easy to clean surface, and will not get deformed due to the super soft silicone. In addition, the palette is designed to be flat and stable, reducing the risk of toppling or spilling during the application process. This MIA Lamitab Organizer provides the utmost comfort, convenience and aesthetic appeal in one package.

 

The Pro Palette Features:

  • 3 cells for steps 1-2-3
  • Section for water/ veil
  • Section for tint with replaceable tint cells
  • 2 cells for liquid glue and glue balm
  • Tool compartment

description:

Thuya Brow paste is used to outline the eyebrow area helping you to achieve quality and consistent shaping results. It also protects the skin during tinting application.

Thuya Brow paste creates a protective barrier on the skin preventing the tint from staining outside the outlined areas. Castor oil extract hydrates and nourishes the outlined skin.

Apply the tint, or, perform an eyebrow shaping procedure.
Remove the tint after recommended exposure time with wet cotton.

name: Thuya Brow Lamination Neutralizer Cream VEGAN - Step 2, 10 Ml
description:
Size 10ml

FOR PROFESSIONAL USE ONLY

Made in Spain
short_description:
The complete efficacy of our neutralizer without any ingredient of animal origin.

The neutralizer is essential to fix the shape of the hair once we have opened the cuticle with the permanent gel.

Its cream texture avoids drips, making application easier, more comfortable and safer.

It allows us to seal and give the desired shape to create the perfect look.

name: Thuya Perming Kit / Brow Lamination Set VEGAN
description:
Thuya Professional Line Vegan Brow Lamination.

Thuya's new vegan lamination kit - a top-quality product line that is fully vegan. Enjoy the same processing times and long-lasting results as our original line, but with the added benefit of being 100% vegan.
short_description:
NEW VEGAN LAMINATION KIT 

The Thuya Lamination Kit includes all three full-size solutions, enough to perform up to 55 brow and lash lift treatments.

N.1 VEGAN PERMANENT GEL

A NEW permanent gel without the animal ingredient and painting its function 100%, thus achieving a product of the same quality and effectiveness but completely vegan. The Permanent Gel opens the hair cuticle, allowing to modify its structure in order to perform the lifting and perm services.

N.2 VEGAN NEUTRALIZER CREAM

The Neutralizer Cream it’s used to perform the lifting and perming services. It has a creamy texture that prevents it from leaking and makes it easier to apply. It’s comfortable and safe with white colour that allows to control its application.

N.3 VEGAN REGENERATING CREAM

The final step of the lamination process! It hydrates and strengthens the renovation and reparation of eyelashes in a natural way.

name: Thuya Brow Lamination Permanent Gel VEGAN - Step 1, 15ml
description:
Dermatologically and Ophthalmologically tested.

Gentle and effective, the final results are excellent, distinctive and unique.

short_description:
Noemi Super Sticky Strong is the latest formula developed by us from the classic “Glue Balm” or Glue without Glue”.
This formula is suitable for everyone and is particularly popular because the eyelashes do not come off the pad so easily.
New formula and stronger, for everyone those who didn’t manage to work with the classic glue balm.

Noemi was the first to develop/invent an eyelash lifting glue, in the form of a balm rich in vitamins and nutrients, which, unlike normal eyelash glues, prevents the eyelashes from drying out and does not dry completely during the treatment.

You know it yourself, one doesn’t stick, the other stinks, the other dries too quickly, etc.
Now here is the solution, our latest invention from the Noemi series:
The revolutionary lashlifting #noemisupersticky is a hybrid glue without glue – but works like a glue to attach the eyelashes to the silicone pad. Because the vitamins and nutrients penetrate the lashes and provide deep moisture, excess “Gluebalm” does not need to be removed. This also results in a faster procedure time and the eyelash lift becomes easier and much faster. It protects the eyelashes from the chemical process and does not allow them to dry out

A plus point of this unique formula is that it doesn’t dry completely during the treatment, so you can still make adjustments as you stretch your lashes.

size 25g

name: Noemi Brow Primer, 50ml
short_description:
The primer prepares the skin before coloring the eyebrows. It gently cleanses, nourishes and regenerates the skin without leaving it greasy or sticky. Makes the color on the hair and skin more natural.

The consistency is gel-like and the scent is pleasant.

Application: Apply to the eyebrows with a cotton pad or cotton swab, do not rinse.

Shelf life: 24 months

Size: 50ml

name: Noemi Shampoo Foam, 50ml
short_description:

﻿﻿In addition, the shampoo gently cleans and cares for the natural eyelashes, eyelash extensions and eyebrows.

Ideal for daily care and cleaning.

Quality from Germany: oil-free – EO & paraben-free – vegan – pH skin-neutral. Considered one of the best in Germany, according to many of our customers.

name: Noemi Lash And Brow Lift Sachet
short_description:
Lotion 1 is the first step in eyelash or brow lifting after the eyelashes have been attached to the silicone pad. It opens the hair structure and the eyelashes/eyebrows are brought into the desired shape. Due to its short exposure time of 5 to 8 minutes, you not only save time, you will also achieve a guaranteed result.

The fix lotion is the next step after the perming lotion. It neutralizes the hair and closes the eyelashes/eyebrows in their new shape. The exposure time is 5 to 8 minutes. The lotion always stays fresh in the practical sachets.

The Nourish is applied as the last step after lifting or coloring. It contains important ingredients, including keratin, which gives the hair care and moisture after a lift. Gently loosens and removes the silicone pads from the eyelids.

name: Noemi Lash And Brow Hybrid Dye (9 colors + color corrector)
short_description:
The Noemi Dye are hybrid colors. Due to the perfect composition of the colors, it finally simplifies the coloring of eyebrows and eyelashes. The colors can be used 100% pure without getting an unwanted yellow, red or green tint. The colors can also be mixed with each other to obtain special mixtures. In addition, they do not darken the eyebrows, because the color lightens the natural hair 1-2 shades beforehand. So you always have the perfect and desired result.

Advantages of this hybrid color are that it conditions and colors the hair. It protects against hair breakage, gives fullness, shine and stimulates hair growth. It leaves a tattoo effect on the skin. The colors contain henna extract, olive oil, green tea and aloe vera.

Available in 9 great colors.

Vegan!

The Noemi Clear is a neutral color corrector. It can be added to any other shade to lighten the colors and it can also be used to enhance the hair and give it extra shine.

With an exposure time of 10 minutes, you get a natural effect that is completely sufficient for coloring the eyebrows.
With an exposure time of 15 minutes, you get an intensive effect on the skin.

Mixing ratio: 1:1 (Solution : Dye)

Exposure time 10 – 15 min.

With an exposure time of 10 minutes, you get a natural effect that is completely sufficient for coloring the eyebrows.

With an exposure time of 15 minutes, you get an intensive effect on the skin.

name: BrowXenna - Henna 10ml
description:
BrowXenna eyebrow henna is…
the first brand on the market created specially for eyebrows on the basis of henna;
the product for eyebrows, which colors not only the hair but also the skin;
coloring product for eyebrows, which is available in 12 shades;
the product, which is chosen by over 20,000 customers in 43 countries;

Instructions for use BrowXenna®

Before coloring:

  • Remove make up carefully, using micellar water. Do not use oil-based means.
  • Prepare eyebrows for coloring. Use BrowXenna® The shampoo-foam for deep cleansing of eyebrows. Shampoo gently and deeply cleanses the hair of the eyebrows and the skin surface, has the effect of light peeling, gently re¬moves dead skin particles, contributing to better fixation of the color.
  • Rinse the shampoo Two-phase fixing tonic, BrowXenna®.

Mixture preparation:

  • In a non-metallic container, mix the coloring composition (the amount of coloring composition is equivalent to 2 rice grains) with 4-8 drops of Mineral solution, BrowXenna®. The mineral solution does not contain impurities, additives or metals. It guarantees that the desired hue will be achieved and extends coloring.
  • Mix the resulting composition thoroughly. If necessary, add solution or coloring composition to the mixture to obtain the desired consistency of soy sauce.

Eyebrow tinting:

  • Using a brush, apply a thin layer of the mixture (try to avoid making spots or gaps) on the skin and hair, to create an ombre effect. Pay special attention to the symmetry and definition of the lines.
  • For a well-defined and even result, apply coloring composition BrowXenna® in several layers.
  • Wait till the layer dries before applying the next layer.
  • Carefully apply the coloring composition, lifting the hair of thick eyebrows with a brush. Spread the color evenly.
  • After complete drying of the last layer moisten the composition and remove from the eyebrows with a cotton pad moistened with a Two-phase fixing tonic, BrowXenna®. To obtain a more intense result of coloring, the time of application of the composition on the eyebrows can reach 25 minutes from the moment of application of the first layer.
short_description: BrowXenna® eyebrow henna is an innovative coloring product based on ground henna leaves, a mixture of herbs and organic compounds for lasting brow coloring with the effect of tattooing. Rich palette of natural shades can be used individually or combined with each other. Natural ingredients of brow henna BrowXenna® take care of damaged and weak hair, strengthening them more and more with each procedure and restoring the natural shape of the eyebrows. The look becomes more expressive and attractive.

name: LeviSsime Lash Activator Oxidant
description:
Oxide 1.8% to activate the coloring elements of the LeviSsime dye. It does not harm the skin and hairs. The components of the composition help reduce possible itching, burning and irritation, have an anti-inflammatory effect. The creamy emulsion is consumed economically and is very easily diluted with paint, and the resulting mixture does not flow and is not lubricated. The volume of the bottle is enough for up to 250 procedures.
Application
Mix LeviSsime paint with this oxide in a 1: 1 ratio to a uniform texture. Apply the mixture to pre-prepared eyebrows and eyelashes. Remove excess immediately with a cotton swab. Wait 15 minutes, then rinse thoroughly with water and blot the remaining moisture with a tissue.

name: LB Lash Brow Regenerating Concentrate Botox
description:
How does Lash Botox “Regenerating Booster” work:
Aimed primarily at filling damaged parts of the eyelash - Restorative effect is achieved. Eyelashes immediately look more dense, voluminous and healthy.
Atelocollagen in the formulation of botox makes lashes shinier.
Creates a thin protective layer on them. Regenerating Booster formula is enriched with 5 oils: castor, argan, almond, macadamia and jojoba. They nourish the eyelashes, make them more elastic, stronger and eliminate their fragility.
Also contains aloe juice, betaine, panthenol (vitamin B5), hydrolyzed wheat proteins and hydrate of rice proteins, tocopherol acetate and vitamin A.
Enhances the nutritional effect of botox.
Saturates the hairs with moisture and softens them.
Does not need to be diluted like regular botox, but effect is still bright and noticeable. Enough for 65-80 procedures.
To make the formulation “stay” longer on the lashes and so that it doesn’t wash off, combine the botox procedure with lamination.
To achieve the maximum therapeutic effect, carry out a complex of 3-4 procedures (depending on the condition of the customer’s eyelashes) with an interval of 2-3 weeks.
short_description:
Regenerating Booster formula consists of 75% natural ingredients.
0.2 ml per procedure.
1 tube is enough for 65-80 procedures!

name: Katya Vinog lash lift pallete
description:
Palette has 5 sections:
1 - solution nr. 1.
2 - solution nr. 2.
3 (Кл) - glue (due to unique shape of the section - glue will not be drying up for up to 1 hour).
4 (B) - water or solution nr. 3 (nourishing product).
5 (Б, Кр) - tint + oxidant.

After performing the treatment wash the palette with warm water immediately to make the cleaning process easier. Please note that tint will be absorbed into the silicone in a few uses but that will not affect the quality of the palette.
short_description:
Katya Vinog silicone palette helps you to perform any lash lift treatment quickly and comfortably by having a space for all products. Keep your station clean and well organised with this beautiful tiffany or black colour palette!
This palette will help you reduce usage of your lash lift products by 30% – that means you can perform more treatments. Fill all sections with your products at the beginning of the treatment – that will reduce the treatment time as well as kipping your work space clean and organised.

name: Lamitta Laminator Brush For Lash Lift
short_description:
Lash Laminator tool is a game changer for the lash lift treatments.

The unique tool is in many aspects a must-have lash lifting tool.

-Now you do not need plenty of tools to make the correct and quick laying of the eyelashes on the shield. The laminator easily lifts the lashes. Makes excellent lash tension and separates them. Copes with any lashes. Comfortable to work on any silicon shields.
-Speed is the most important quality of this tool. Adhering eyelashes to the shields speeds up all the process of lash lifting. You will save time. The procedure will go much faster. Lash lifting is easy and fast!
-Safe and not painful. The laminator is based on bristles that gently work with eyelashes without damaging them and is absolutely safe when working with the eyes.
-It is enough to soak the brush in any available disinfector for brushes and tools.
-Laminator is not a disposable tool! Excellent quality allows you to use it for a very long time. At least half a year till a year this brush will serve you every day.
-Use – wash – disinfect – dry – repeat.
By buying Laminator, you will be able to do lash lamination quickly, efficiently, safely and economically!

name: Thuya Eyebrow Bleaching Solution, 15ml
description:
How to use:

Mix Thuya Bleach Solution with Thuya Cream Oxidant in 1:1 ratio until smooth
Prepare, clean and degrease the skin the skin and apply the mixture with the brush for 10 minutes
After processing time is finishes, clean the eyebrows with a damp cotton pad
short_description:
It is recommended to use Thuya Bleaching solution with Special Dye Solution Oxidant (Cream).

Thuya Bleach is used for:

– for lightening natural eyebrows 1-2 tones
– for lightening dark eyebrows and subsequent tinting in the desired tone of a lighter shade
– for leveling the color of grey or uneven eyebrows

Shelf life after opening is 12 months. Store in a dark place. The lid must be firmly closed.

Note! It is necessary to remove the protective ring from the dye to avoid oxidation.

This new and innovative Colour Active formula provides an even, long lasting colour.

short_description:
Thuya Neturalizer Cream is Step 2 in Brow Lamination Treatment.

name: Thuya Brow Lamination Permanent Gel - Step 1, 15ml
description:
Dermatologically and Ophthalmologically tested.

Gentle and effective, the final results are excellent, distinctive and unique.

Odor during the procedure is the release of sulfur-hydrogen and is absolutely normal for such procedures in accordance with chemical processes.
Size 15ml

FOR PROFESSIONAL USE ONLY

Made in Spain
short_description:
Thuya Permanent Gel, Step 1 in Eyebrow Lamination Treatment.

Permanent gel solution reacts by chemically softening the inner structure of the hair by breaking some of the cross links within and between the protein chains of the hair. The hair swells, stretches and softens.

Processing times 10-15 minutes.

name: Thuya Perming Kit / Brow Lamination Set
description:
Step 1 Thuya Permanent Gel (Processing times 10-15 minutes)

Permanent gel solution reacts by chemically softening the inner structure of the hair by breaking some of the cross links within and between the protein chains of the hair. The hair swells, stretches and softens.

Step 2 Neutralizer Cream (Processing times 10-15 minutes)

Neutralizer Cream is then applied to “set” the new shape of the hair by reinserting the cross linking bonds.

Step 3 Thuya Regenerating Cream

Regenerating cream seals the result from first and second steps. Naturally moisturizes the eyebrows. Vitamin E improves the hair structure and some of its internal characteristics. It nourishes, moisturizes the hair, as well as protects them from the harmful effects of the environment.

Argan oil contains more than 80% of polyunsaturated omega-6 fatty acids and has a high content of vitamins A, E, F. It is ideal for maintaining and enhancing the effect of coloring procedures and lamination of the eyebrows.

Neutralizer and Regenerating creams will help neutralize any remaining alkalinity affecting your skin's optimal pH level after the Brow Lamination procedure.
Thuya regenerating cream needs to stay on for 24 hours.

Processing times for Permanent Gel and Neutralizer cream are 10-15 minutes each depending on the thickness of the eyebrow hairs.

Thuya Client After Care:

Do not get your eyelashes or eyebrows wet for at least 24 hours after the treatment.

Do not have a hot bath/shower or use a sauna, steam room or swimming pool for 24 hours.

Avoid eye make up for 12 hours. Try to use oil free makeup remover at all times.

To avoid irritation, do not rub or touch the eye or eyebrow area.

Don’t spend too long in direct sunlight as this will weaken the perm effect and fade the tint color.

Chlorine and certain skincare products will shorten the effects of the perm and tints.
FOR PROFESSIONAL USE ONLY

Made in Spain
short_description:
Thuya Lamination Kit includes all three full size solutions, enough to perform up to 55 treatments!

The kit contains :

– Thuya Permanent gel, 15 ml.
– Thuya Neutralizer cream, 10 ml.
– Thuya Regenerating Argan cream, 15 ml.

name: Lash&Go Cream Remover Ariel 15g
description:
Make removal process super comfortable: the product does not cause irritation
How to use:
Using a micro brush, apply a thin layer of the remover directly onto the glue bonds. Leave for up to 5 min (depending on the volume of extensions and how fresh the set is, and the amount of glue used) and remove gently with dry brushes or tweezers. Ensure that both remover and adhesive are fully removed with dry brushes prior to use of other products.
PLEASE NOTE: Remover should be carefully applied to avoid the contact with the skin or eyes.

FOR PROFESSIONAL USE ONLY

Volume 15ml
short_description:
Creamy remover with a light cherry aroma for professional removal of eyelash extensions.

The dense texture of the cream almost completely eliminates the risk of contact with the product in the eyes.

name: Browxenna® Ruler With A Stretched Thread
description:
Instructions for use:
Disinfect a thread before the procedure or use a special thread for eyebrow threading. Fix one end of the thread into the slot of the ruler. Stretch the thread and fix it in the second slot. Check that the thread does not sag.

Color the thread using a pencil for eyebrows Lena Levi or Contour white paste for eyebrows BrowXenna®. Mark the control points of the future shape of the eyebrows and connect them. Control points are marked in accordance with the formula which the master has chosen. To make the line even, put the ruler perpendicular to the face — so that the thread touches the area between the two control points. Gently press on the thread and draw a line.

After the markup is complete, remove the thread from the ruler. A new thread should be used for each customer.

Ruler and thread disinfection:

  • Disinfect a thread before the procedure or use a special thread for eyebrow threading.

Thread fixation

  • Fix one end of the thread into the slot of the ruler. Stretch the thread and fix it in the second slot. Check that the thread does not sag.

Thread coloring

  • Color the thread using a pencil for eyebrows Lena Levi or Contour white paste for eyebrows BrowXenna®.

Outlining the control points of the future eyebrow’s shape and their connection

  • Mark the control points of the future shape of the eyebrows and connect them. Control points are marked in accordance with the formula which a master has chosen. To make the line even, put the ruler perpendicular to the face — so that the thread touches the area between the two control points. Gently press on the thread and draw a line.

Thread removal

  • After the markup is completed, remove the thread from the ruler. A new thread should be used for each customer.

Thread for the ruler is not included.
short_description:
Ruler with a stretched thread is an ideal tool for creating eyebrow’s shape sketches. It helps to mark control points of the future eyebrow’s form and check the symmetry.

The BrowXenna® ruler is designed specially to fit the clients face, so it does not cause discomfort. The measurement scale helps the master to make a symmetrical sketch of the eyebrows, and the colored thread stretched on the base of the instrument — to create clear and even lines.

The ruler is made of durable material and does not deform when the thread is stretched.

name: BrowXenna® Contour White Paste For Eyebrows Mapping 10g
description:
Instructions for use:
There are two ways to work with Contour white paste for eyebrows, BrowXenna®.

  • Using beveled brush apply the paste directly to the skin, use it to mark the future shape.
  • Firstly, create a sketch with a pencil, and on top of the pencil lines apply white paste. To make the sketch smooth and clear, place the brush with the paste on the pencil line, and stretch the paste down or up from the line. Do not pull the brush along the pencil sketch — the paste will not lie tight enough.

Ingredients: Neopentyl Glycol Diethylhexanoate, Jojoba Esters, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax, Nylon-12, Beeswax, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Silica, Boron Nitride, Stearyl Dimethicone, Cyclopentasiloxane, Tocopheryl Acetate, Sodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Titanium Dioxide.

Volume: 10 g
Applying: Brows
short_description: Contour white paste for eyebrows, BrowXenna® is an indispensable tool when drawing a sketch of eyebrows shape before coloring. It allows to build a perfect symmetry of the eyebrows. Prevents from spreading of the coloring composition during the coloring procedure, thus protecting the skin that should not be colored. White paste has a thick, non-greasy cream consistency. Easily applied on the skin without burdening or tightening it, suitable for all skin types.

name: BrowXenna® Perfect Bleach Set
description:
Use for bleaching:

  • unwanted dark hair on the face and body
  • natural eyebrows, the color of which is very different from the color of the hair. For example, bleached blondes
  • tinted eyebrows if the shade is too dark

Benefits:

  • quickly, safely and delicately bleaches the hair on the face and body
  • allows you to achieve intense hair bleaching by 4 tones
  • eliminates the unwanted appearance of a yellow tint after bleaching
  • does not create a feeling of skin tightness due to the moisturizing ingredients in the composition
  • suitable for home use

How to use:

  • Clean the bleaching area with water and let it dry
  • Mix BrowXenna® OXYGEN J2 Cream-activator 2.7% with the PERFECT BLEACH bleaching powder in ratio 1:1 in a non-metallic container. Stir until smooth and leave the mixture for 30 seconds for all components to fully interact
  • Apply the paste so that it completely covers the hair from roots to ends. Soak the cream for not more than 10 minutes: 7-8 minutes — on light hair, 9-10 minutes — on dark hair
  • Check the bleaching process every 2-3 minutes
  • Thoroughly rinse the bleaching mixture off hair and skin with plenty of water
  • Blot the hair with a dry cloth
  • Tint the eyebrows with dye If necessary. For example, use BrowXenna® Oxygen J2 dye
  • Apply a moisturizing lotion or cream to your skin after bleaching your face and body hair

ATTENTION!
Before applying the cream, test for sensitivity of the skin to the components of the product. To do this, mix a small amount of the product and apply to a 1 cm2 area of skin on the inner surface of the hand. Wait 10 minutes and rinse off with cold water. If redness, irritation or inflammation appears within 24 hours, the product must not be used. If there are no signs, use PERFECT BLEACH as described in the instruction.

Volume: 50 g
short_description:

  • BrowXenna® PERFECT BLEACH bleaching powder, 20 g

  • Measuring spoon

PERFECT BLEACH bleaching powder delicately acts on hair: it does not damage them and does not dry out.
